Subject: [MediaTek] FSAC Bulkimport Time out
Description:
Hi Support,

Here is an issue reported by Mediatek  regarding FSAC Bulkimport job time out,Please help to clarify it asap.

Jimmy
What_We_Know__c: The customer was facing FSAC execution timeout errors initially. Those were resolved by increasing timeout settings at the Job level and the scheduled task level. Afterwards, the customer was facing issue with error of insufficient disk space. Increasing the disk space resolved the issue.
Solution_Comment__c: The customer was facing FSAC execution timeout errors initially. Those were resolved by increasing timeout settings at the Job level and the scheduled task level. Afterwards, the customer was facing issue with error of insufficient disk space. Increasing the disk space resolved the issue.
